reviewText: A Look into the 1798 battle of the Nile which ended Napoleon's Attempt to end  England's trade with india by seizing egypt

Not much detective work with the show going from a couple of dives re-discovering the L'Orient, how?  By simply asking one of the host's friend who was on a 1980's expedition that made the original discovery.  They make a point to tell how the L'Orient exploded, but don't add ANY new info on the subject nor any new analysis.
overall a very lame espd.
